ol.li:
non-financial contracts, such as:
purchase or sales contracts where quantities are in excess of purchase, sale or usage requirements, and where the contract can be net settled (no physical delivery);
commodity contracts;
public-private partnership (P3) contracts;
insurance contracts; or
contracts involving payments based on a climatic or geological variable.

Inflation index: cash flows that are adjusted by:
inflation indices based on Canadian or non-Canadian rates, or
leveraged inflation and CPI adjustments (factor above 2);

Call, put, prepayment or redemption option that requires the payment of a penalty that:
is fixed, or
varies based on current interest rates or some other variable;
